dcterms:description: The dataset contains traffic data, geometrical data, and social data. The traffic data includes Entry and Exit data for each station at five time stamps, namely Early, AM, Mid, PM, and Late, based on yearly average scale over 13 years (2003-2012 and 2014-2016). For this study, stations within Zone 4 (206 in total) are used.
dcterms:title: VIS-tube project
